    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The processing of flax, hemp, cotton, or another fiber by separating the fine fibers from the impurities such as the seeds, straw, and woody stems.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
